\bra{0} \a_{p_2'}^B \a_{p_1'}^A \tfrac{i}{2} ( \bar{\psi}^{A'} \Gamma \psi^{A'}) (\bar{\psi}^{B'} \Gamma \psi^{B'})(\adag_{p_1})^A(\adag_{p_2})^B \ket{0} & = 
\contraction{\a_{p_2'}}{ \a_{p_1'}}{\tfrac{i}{2} ( }{\bar{\psi}}
